{"tid":1346403,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唔撚該你班撚樣學下班保皇狗","createTime":"2019-07-22T04:06:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T06:34:16.000Z","uid":126115,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a85c144539ed97c452c3056f197ef75f901285e2","tid":1346403,"uid":126115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:06:21.000Z","msg":"何妖 黑警 鄉黑 夾埋係元朗搞恐怖襲擊<br />\n第二日 保皇狗出黎繼續出黎開記者會指鹿為馬 癲倒是非黑白<br />\n<br />\n割席何妖？ 冇<br />\n指責黑警？ 冇<br />\n譴責鄉黑？ 冇<br />\n<br />\n今日開始 唔撚該你地係咩立場好 <br />\n學下班保皇狗永遠槍口對外 十隻手指指撚住對家<br />\n無論議員 武勇 和理非 咩人都好 做左咩你唔認同既事都好<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n不指責<br />\n不分化<br />\n不篤灰</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"a8e617406789ea540da031997af9bb6c25b1fd48","tid":1346403,"uid":126115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:06:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adbf1c99ba7b87f9c8c238e28137cc316ba81391","tid":1346403,"uid":126115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:07:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ad50316ce3f531b9f32484d7f9de1df0f8b2edf","tid":1346403,"uid":126115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:07:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65afd4d79b983a0ed82ebf8da959d55ba93612fe","tid":1346403,"uid":126115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:07:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8de8e35e6ca29569394f1bf2322a5492e7f62a2b","tid":1346403,"uid":207208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:08:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">VW9089<br />\nWZ7266<br />\nNT21<br />\nVL9886<br />\n成班白衣打人嗰啲車牌<br />\n幫share</span></span>"},{"pid":"0b20cfc58078